race.comment: KHABERNI (2) Was competitive when 2nd last start at this track. Camilio Ospina and Ahmed Mohamoud deserve serious consideration as a team. Running with confidence since resuming from a break. One of the major players. ALANZAE ALBATEEN (9) Racing fresh today after a break of 37 weeks. Displayed potential when winning last time at the track and good career start. Demonstrating upward trajectory in recent races. Deserves consideration. LILAELYA (12) First up after a 52 week break. Strong performance to win last run around here and putting a tidy record together so far. Will have to carry more weight. No surprise to see a forward showing and one of the main hopes in this race. SIMEEHAAN (15) Finished 3rd last time at the track and has a positive stall. Bit of extra work to do with more weight. Appears well in this.
